text: Feeling Minnesota is a 1996 American romantic comedy-drama crime movie starring Cameron Diaz, Dan Aykroyd and Courtney Love. It was released in the USA on September 13, 1996, and is about confusion and problems in romance decisions. ==References== == Other websites == * Category:1996 comedy-drama movies Category:1996 crime drama movies Category:1990s criminal comedy movies Category:1996 romantic comedy movies Category:American crime drama movies Category:American criminal comedy movies Category:American romantic comedy movies Category:American romantic drama movies Category:1990s English-language movies Category:Movies set in Minnesota
